description:
RATIONAL FUNK is a complete instructional program for musicians of all skill levels, featuring tips, tricks, inspiration, and industry secrets from acclaimed drum professional Dave King (The Bad Plus). 

In this episode, Dave talks about:
• day drinking
• Dr. Kalstrup
• Tim Berne

Shot by Noah Hutton 
Edited by Joe Johnson

Learn more:
http://rationalfunk.tv
http://daveking.net
http://thebadplus.com

Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/rationalfunk

Hit SUBSCRIBE to hear about new episodes.

Dave King plays Rat Rod Drums and Zildjian cymbals with Vic Firth Sticks.
http://zildjian.com
http://vicfirth.com
